116
00:06:43,208 --> 00:06:47,803
dos vos ikh gedenk, dos lebn in geto, dos tog-teglekhe lebn,

117
00:06:48,112 --> 00:06:50,343
iz eh geven nor a geyeg

118
00:06:50,343 --> 00:06:53,014
far dem shpayz, zikh oystsuhaltn.

119
00:06:53,776 --> 00:06:56,311
der tate, ammerstn der tate,

